Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.36,0:00:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin Okumura, the son of Satan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukio...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mephisto?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Pages! Thank you for your good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think I'd allow demons over mid-class to enter the Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctors, please tend to the wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprise! I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:01:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This training camp was your Esquire exam at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,During the camp, teachers were observing and testing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll decide your final grades after reading their reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for the announcement, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:03:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it was a surprise exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They had us completely fooled...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We should've considered it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pointless to worry about that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to you and Shima,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I did hardly anything worth mentioning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Okumura told us right before the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,An Exorcist cannot fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...get on well and cool your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They tested our qualities for Esquire in a real battle situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But in that case, I was the worst of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two just sat back and did absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have anything to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! I got the Claw of the Scaly Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, stupid brat! There's nothing I'd want to talk about with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He talked! He was so mysterious all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so good at ventriloquism!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... Sorry. I woke you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I'm more or less fine by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,About the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get the best grade, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even want to imagine what would have happened without you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That... no! I should thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pass, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Or we all are failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Okumura, how did you defeat that Ghoul?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:05:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I just... slashed it with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! You're really fit for a Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Slashed it with that? Would it hurt to be more specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the greatest mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just look at me, I'm a great mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistletoe... Mistilteinn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean mysterious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a Page but he defeated a mid-class demon without support.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And with a sword? Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He really is a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Neuhaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,May we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your actions yesterday clearly deviated from the arrangements of the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,True, there were other teachers on the watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but independently putting a student in danger like that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,risked the exam itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried to make Rin Okumura use his powers in front of other students.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a selected few teachers know about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Pheles should have briefed you on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I acted as I was ordered by Sir Pheles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to kill him, he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you're acting as the brake to his powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I was chosen as the accelerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was to understand Rin Okumura's powers as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon was examined to find out if he's fit for use as a weapon of the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You little genius of an Exorcist are always so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:07:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,At least share the burden of watching over a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother is in relatively good control of his powers and emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,At least for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have seen that yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate his abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's not like I'd actually kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday was tough, wasn't it, Ni?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Shiemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:08:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disturb you this late. Is the Manager here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She went to stock up so I'm taking care of the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah! It's just the two of us! Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't enter the cram school determined to become an Exorcist like the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so I didn't really know what to choose...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing to be so half-hearted about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiemi, do you remember our first meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I had just become an Exorcist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't freak out. Where will you end up if you're already so anxious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a supply store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you about Yukio earlier and today I brought him with me. He's an Exorcist from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not even 14 yet, so take good care of him for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Nice to meet you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So young and yet so splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right, Shiemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiemi, come out for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Shiemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She could be mistaken for a household spirit, couldn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my daughter, but she's way too shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiemi, he's the same age as you but he's an Exorcist teacher already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello... I'm Yukio Okumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's as shy as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... I hoped she'd be interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with your work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds so strange, just call me casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I call you Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... it sounds cute... really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was so terrible back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally admired you! I thought you were amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not that impressive a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was little I was a crybaby, and my brother had to help me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He was always doing stuff I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So back then I admired him a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin is so kind, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But people can't stay children forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you've worked hard to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But you need determination to continue further with your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:12:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even more now that you know you have talent as a Tamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk it through with the Manager and decide before tomorrow's announcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,With Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If you become an Esquire, you have to be prepared to risk your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You need the consent of your guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,During that test I thought it was useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry that it ended up a bit tougher than it should've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But a test is a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was controlled not to go beyond a certain level... supposedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The teachers were there to ensure your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's not like I'd actually kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you wouldn't kill him, Mr. Neuhaus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid, Yukio Okumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:28.02,Default,,0,0,20,,Shi-Shiemi?! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:29.89,Default,,0,0,20,,Were you trying to seduce me in my sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:34.38,Default,,0,0,20,,You wouldn't wake up, so Yuki carried you to another room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,20,,He told me to just stay he{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is killing my brother necessary to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it is here. For wherever the carcass is, there will the eagles be gathered together.{ Matthew 24:28}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the strongest Naberius I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could just erase the circle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You were an enemy after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Filthy demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy water works, even though you wear a human skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hide your true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy water? As if...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You erased it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll damage your body if you try to summon another.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to die of blood loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a survivor of the Blue Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Blue Night...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Blue Night took place 16 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,when Satan simultaneously slaughtered many of the world's prominent clergymen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For a moment Satan possessed my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and my family who tried to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Satan used my own hands to kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never forgive Satan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor any of his demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And definitely not the son of Satan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it costs my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If this still isn't enough for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight you as many times as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to this shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drag innocent people into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As if you'd get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There are others like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki?! Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Neuhaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's closing already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My wounds have always healed fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really a beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki! Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiemi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A Ghoul wound! That must be treated right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lie down here, right now! Don't overdo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lie down already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ni, can you give me some sancho?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks... I'm fine already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He is always doing stuff I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no match to him after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eins, zwei, drei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You all passed! Congratulations, Esquires!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To celebrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have pancakes!{monja}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:21:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Pancakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we at least have barbeque?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You as an Exorcist...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll help everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you fight at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about professor Neuhaus' actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think a teacher would get so carried away by emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prevent further events like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Okumura, are you okay with lemonade?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, lemonade's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Neuhaus did just as I instructed him, but apparently it was too much for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to True Cross Academy right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't enter the campus because of your barriers, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Neuhaus will lead you through.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll talk about the details later. Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, looks so yummy! I'll help myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi! Wait a second, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Father and Brother are so obsessed with this Rin Okumura. I wonder how strong he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope he'll be good to kill my boredom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.49,0:24:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's have some...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheese, pork and mochi pancake is one of my top three favorites!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.41,0:24:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be the Principal, but this is first come, first serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.63,0:24:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot! Too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.91,0:24:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You will kill it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.02,0:24:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no Exorcist at the Academy able to tame a demon of that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.66,0:24:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro is dead. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.03,0:24:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're liars!
