Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:31.52,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,sei wo uke sorezore ga jinsei wo ouka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:34.15,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,nou no black box wo shiru sore wa kou ka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:36.70,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,you wa limit line wo subete ryouga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:39.66,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,saa ikou ka fumidasu sore wa kyou da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:44.95,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,yappa hibi wa ika sen kou sotsunaku konashitecha no no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:50.08,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,stop nagare wo mikiwamena mazu mono to mo sezu ikou ze (here we go)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:54.84,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,todokanu mono ya kagiri aru mono ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:59.43,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,atsuku naru mune wo osaetsukeru no wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:04.94,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,rikai mo sezu osaetsukeyou to shitekita
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:08.81,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,ano otonatachi to onaji jan ka yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:13.90,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,doushitatte kanawanai esoragoto darou ga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:18.40,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,mune wo moyasu hi wa dare ni mo keseya shinai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:23.66,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,sora kara furu kuroi ame ga kono mi nurashi furitomanakutomo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:29.08,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,mada ore wa kawareru jibun de kaetemiseru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:34.55,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}kore ga sou "pride" sorezore no basho de
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:38.88,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,717)}mada mada kieru na kokoro no hi wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:44.35,OPromaji,,0,0,0,,mada mada ikeru zo ikeru zo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:31.52,OP,,0,0,0,,After birth, people live as they wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:34.15,OP,,0,0,0,,They then learn the black box in their head; is that bliss?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:36.70,OP,,0,0,0,,Just cross over, beyond the line of your limit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:39.66,OP,,0,0,0,,Let's go, take a step, and I mean this minute
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:44.95,OP,,0,0,0,,Life's a bitch, so if it's easy, you're doing it wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:50.08,OP,,0,0,0,,Stop, which way is the world going? Then ignore it and go wherever (here we go)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:54.84,OP,,0,0,0,,There are things I could never have, things with time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:59.43,OP,,0,0,0,,Is there a reason I force my heart upon them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:04.94,OP,,0,0,0,,I never tried to understand, I just forced it on them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:08.81,OP,,0,0,0,,I'm no better than those lifeless adults
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:13.90,OP,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just a pipe dream I could never have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:18.40,OP,,0,0,0,,But no one can put out the fire in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:23.66,OP,,0,0,0,,The black rain may pour hard and leave me drenched
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:29.08,OP,,0,0,0,,But I know I can change, I will change myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:34.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}This is my pride, what makes up my core
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:38.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,15)}I won't let my fire be put out; not yet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:44.35,OP,,0,0,0,,I'll keep going, and I'll never stop
